Ever since I started using Caddy, doing that has been soooo easy.<p>Download the binary, make a Caddyfile</p><p></p><pre><code>  myservice.example.com {
   basic_auth {
    admin some_password_hash_here
   }
   reverse_proxy :3000
  }
</code></pre>
And then just "./caddy start"

